u don''t accept, it goes to someone else.', 589, 0), (124327, 'Words give sound to the beauty of Life.', 4406, 0), (124328, 'Shifting perspective(s) and being proactive are essential to your our life paths, progress and possibilities: "Just because a door appears closed it does not mean that it is locked - nor that it will not open with the right heart, call or touch', 4889, 0), (124329, 'Until you are clear nothing will be. The moment you are clear everything will be.', 4889, 0), (124330, 'Being a good leader does not require you possessing a fancy title, no more than possessing a fancy title makes you a good leader.', 5237, 0), (124331, 'Not only a man without hand is handicapped but also a man without health.', 589, 0), (124332, 'Your heart can be broken, but your soul never bleeds.', 2111, 0), (124333, 'We need at least one enemy to know our own stuff>>>', 24106, 0), (124334, 'If you make your own path in this thing we call life, you will forever know that it was yours and not someone else''s. - Michael A. Contés II', 24102, 0), (124335, 'If you make your own path in this thing we call life, you will forever know that it was yours and not someone else''s.', 24102, 0), (124336, 'In the grand scheme of things it makes no difference who is right but rather what''s right that counts.', 24102, 0), (124337, 'First opportunity is the golden opportunity.', 589, 0), (124338, 'This is not a dirty little secret which was discovered just yesterday. But, if you follow the Golden Rule, good things happen to you and those around you.', 24102, 0), (124339, 'Every great athlete, artist and aspiring being has a great team to help them flourish and succeed - personally and professionally. Even the so-called ''solo star'' has a strong supporting cast helping them shine, thrive and take flight.', 4889, 0), (124340, 'Be kind. Be kind to others, be kind to animals, be kind to yourself. Smile at the mailman, pet your dog, buy yourself an ice cream cone. Spreading kindness in this world is the noblest thing a person can do.', 24107, 0), (124341, 'When everything seems hopeless, turn your mind toward the three people who mean most to you in this world. Think about what you must mean to them, and from those thoughts of those three people will stem all the hope and meaning you’ll need to fight through.', 24107, 0), (124342, 'Let your personality be your profit and not your punishment.', 589, 0), (124343, 'You will breathe throughout your life, every moment of it, but an opportunity like this comes once in a lifetime, and not even to everyone. Go for it!', 15051, 0), (124344, 'Never pass on an opportunity to say thank you or give recognition for a job well done', 5237, 0), (124345, 'A pat on the back can often motivate more than currency notes!', 11305, 0), (124346, 'My two most unproductive days of the week have always been yesterday and tomorrow. Keeping that in mind, I try to focus majority of my attention on today.', 5237, 0), (124347, 'Thought for the day: we have far too many of them. And we prize them too highly; more so than we do the power of silence, mindfulness and pure kindness.', 4889, 0), (124348, 'What makes you successful is other peoples’ success”.', 15335, 0), (124349, 'Familiarity is the dagger thrust into the heart of fear.', 4406, 0), (124350, 'If you try to be everywhere at once, you won''t be anywhere at all.', 4406, 0);
