d. ''There is no difficulty. I can cover 300 miles if necessary. Using assorted religions and their gods, saints, and prophets. Hindu, Sikh, Judaic, Christian, Muslim, Zoroastrian, Buddhist, Jainist. Actually, Hinduism alone can produce enough. But I always like to mix them up, include a variety in my drawings. Makes me feel I am doing something to promote tolerance and understanding in the world.', 3998, 0), (125713, 'The Word of God is my life''s manual.', 19416, 0), (125714, 'I''m more interested in lookin'' forward than back. The past is done and there''s no changin'' it.', 24260, 0), (125715, 'How like God''s love yours has been to me- so wise, so generous, and so unsparing!" exclaimed Pancratius. "Promise me one thing more- that is, that you will stay near to me to the end, and carry my last legacy to my mother.', 11104, 0), (125716, 'Prayer is a powerful weapon.', 2878, 0), (125717, 'Abide in the vine, you will bear much fruits.', 2878, 0), (125718, 'Perfect God, Prince of Peace.', 2878, 0), (125719, 'God is all in all.', 2878, 0), (125720, 'The sinner is saved by the Saviour.', 2878, 0), (125721, 'I''ll try to turn the other cheek....But I''ve only got two and they''re both stinging.', 24260, 0), (125722, 'Nothing good in this world comes free! For everything there’s a payment of time or money or soul!', 19132, 0), (125723, 'The Lord is my shelter.', 2878, 0), (125724, 'Don’t forget the laws of God.', 2878, 0), (125725, 'It takes grace to know the word of truth.', 2878, 0), (125726, 'Seriously brethren, Judas is not in the nightclubs and pool bar right now. He is in the churches. Singing hymns and praying. gentleman indeed. Closest to Believers but the only thing is he wont go on to receive the Holy Ghost. This is a ‪‎healthy‬ ‪information‬ for me because then i will be careful not to be watching and comparing myself with others but instead check myself with the Word.', 18372, 0), (125727, 'Without a regular pay for two years, I appreciate the timeless provi